{"tid":1322842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］新城市廣場根本一早已經plan好咗做戰場！","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:24:20.000Z","uid":274263,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7bea71d485ffc2104349e24de61e45c90a3df398","tid":1322842,"uid":274263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"代朋友post:<br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市廣場中間果位周不時都會起d嘢黎吸引顧客打卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dgkdzag.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgkdzag.png&h=ca261c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個薰衣草展覽7月9日仲起緊，見相都起到七七八八隨時開得迎接weekend<br />\n<br />\n因咩原因7月14日遊行果日就無左架呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定係商場擔心啲薰衣草太危險啦<br />\n但點解商場方面又無啦啦會有這個擔心呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇返佢個facebook, 一切答案已經呼之欲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nSmarTone 5G X Fun 巡禮<br />\n日期及時間： 2019年7月11日至13日<br />\n地址：新城市廣場一期1/F羅馬廣場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4q2juJM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4q2juJM.png&h=5e16a436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家對 #仲夏薰衣緣 活動的支持，作為全港首個室內薰衣草園，為了讓大家體驗一個盡善盡美的浪漫紫色花海，我們決定把「Lavender Romance In Town 仲夏薰衣緣」延期舉行。有關活動的新安排，將會另行通知，敬請密切留意。不便之處，希望大家見諒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfvQBoT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtfvQBoT.png&h=cf48c73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">正常公司邊有人租weekend唔租星期日？仲要Smartone係新鴻基旗下公司</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">專登將兩個場星期日嘅展覽清空左￼<br />\n所有事情都指向一個答案<br />\n就係新城市一早已經ready送你班人去死！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n#早有預謀<br />\n<br />\n沙田友表示，新城市byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42726584ecc3c936958b3a6963ead46de18bc2fd","tid":1322842,"uid":258703,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"班狗phonein電台都認咗同新城市廣場有夾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e45d856da2899a9ffb383645f4ec9e76fe3f7bc","tid":1322842,"uid":83910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"謎底已經解開"},{"pid":"7bf6a351d6f0d86e4acb0a30b806c07053150be6","tid":1322842,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"根本一撚早同黑警夾定<br />\n新鴻基正仆街"},{"pid":"e598be95e50bb5bc43a7ea055d8650f8ebfbb5d4","tid":1322842,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"今日去屌柒佢地"},{"pid":"be9c7c3a895c2caa14bcb4f2dd5888887106dee0","tid":1322842,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3041a4c7f2a286058895fbd05e4c0a0f8958a881","tid":1322842,"uid":137078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321643</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ccf87dc9bb1bc0d4406567e57ca612f9953e08f7","tid":1322842,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E3%80%91%E8%AC%9D%E6%8C%AF%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%BE%88%E6%97%A9%E5%B7%B2%E8%88%87%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E7%B7%8A%E5%AF%86%E8%81%AF%E7